title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Illustrious House of Throwing Fits
description:
There goes the last great American dynasty: Throwing Fits. Third times a charm for The Core Four as the gd mf boys link up and do their damndest to be everything to everyone because that’s just how much they care. Audiophiles rejoice! Topics include, but are not limited to: addressing feedback, constructive criticism, copping new mics, the Throw Gang’s dream guest list, TikTok, digital fashion week, how to make merch, managing expectations, a surprise live reaction to finding out you’re Lil Wayne’s eskimo brother, break up music, Taylor Swift, getting doxxed, the Second Amendment and much more on this Patreon-exclusive episode of Throwing Fits.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
